name: Julian Agudelo
description: Hi my name is Julian Agudelo, I am a  Mechanical Engineer with experience in UI/UX, water and waste water consulting, and process engineering. I graduated from the University of Florida in 2023 with a Bachelors of Science in Mechanical engineering and Project management certificate. I am also certified by the state of Florida as an EIT (Engineer in Training) and am pursuing a Professional Engineering Liscence.
